

'''''Made in Heaven''''' ni filime yikinamico yo muri [[Nigeriya]] yo muri 2019 iyobowe na Toka McBaror ikorwa na Darlington Abuda. Ibiranga Nollywood's Richard Mofe Damijo, Jide Kosoko, and Nancy Isime,<ref name="Pulse2">https://www.pulse.ng/entertainment/movies/toka-mcbaror-films-made-in-heaven-featuring-rmd-nancy-isime/5sq92n2</ref> Ayo Makun, Toyin Abraham, Blossom Chukwujekwu, Lasisi Elenu,<ref name="Gu2">https://m.guardian.ng/art/mofe-damijo-ay-kosoko-light-up-made-in-heaven/</ref> former Big Brother Naija housemate - Kemen,, n'abandi. <ref>https://newsofafrica.org/nigerian-movie-director-toka-mcbaror-films-made-in-heaven-feat-rmd-jide-kosoko-nancy-isime.html</ref> Filime yerekana abantu nyamukuru bashakisha ubufasha bwumwuka mubuzima bwabo bwa buri munsi. <ref name="Re">https://www.independent.ng/nollywood-movie-alert-made-in-heaven/</ref>

== Umugambi ==
Nyuma yo kubona ko umukunzi we amushuka hamwe ninshuti, isoni Richard yamusize inyuma yangwa muri club gusa ahura na Angela bahuye nkibyo. Muri iryo joro nyene, barapfuye hanyuma ku murongo uja ku Irembo ry'Urubanza, Angela asabwa gusubira ku Isi. Richard yahise ashakisha inzira aratoroka kurwanira urukundo rwa Angela, nubwo bibujijwe na malayika murinzi woherejwe nyuma ye hamwe nabadayimoni kugirango atazigera atsindira urukundo rwe muminsi irindwi, kunanirwa bikaba byaviramo ubugingo bwe gucirwaho iteka.<ref>https://bonggis.com/2019/11/made-in-heaven-movie-review/</ref><ref>https://ng.opera.news/ng/en/entertainment/f519c55b4d6f898df9c93b0f1c2b7954</ref>

