Filime yakozwe na Peekaboo Consulting Limited.  Yakoranye na Newlink Entertainment Limited, NewOhens Limited na Corporate World Entertainment Limited. 

== Kurekura ==
Iyi filime yemejwe ko izasohoka mu mpeshyi ya 2019.  Yerekanwe ku cyumweru, tariki ya 15 Nzeri 2019 muri IMAX Theatre, Lekki, Lagos, [[Nijeriya]] .  <ref>https://connectnigeria.com/articles/2019/09/the-made-in-heaven-movie-premiere/</ref> <ref>https://www.qed.ng/ay-makun-toyin-abraham-to-star-in-made-in-heaven/</ref>

